---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Platform Features | ToolGrid" description="Discover the zero-trust architecture and powerful features behind ToolGrid.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl py-20">
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">Platform Features</h1>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-4 text-white">1. Zero-Trust Local Architecture</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg mb-8">Unlike traditional SaaS platforms that force you to upload your sensitive data to their cloud, ToolGrid brings the cloud to you. Every single tool runs strictly inside your local browser using WebAssembly (WASM). When you compress a video or parse a CSV, it never leaves your machine.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-4 text-white">2. Blazing Fast Execution</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg mb-8">By eliminating server round-trips and upload wait times, you get instant feedback. Our heavily optimized WASM engines execute complex tasks—like FFmpeg video rendering and ONNX AI inference—at near-native speeds directly on your hardware.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-4 text-white">3. Completely Free. Unlimited Usage.</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg mb-8">Because you provide the computing power through your own browser, our server costs are nearly zero. We pass these savings directly to you. No subscriptions, no credits, no paywalls, and no artificial limits on file sizes.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-4 text-white">4. No Account Required</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg mb-8">We believe software should be accessible immediately. You don't need to hand over your email, verify an account, or deal with marketing spam just to use a simple utility.</p>
    
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
